STATEMENT 
Statement are the commds using which we can perfrom CURD operations on the database.
1--Data defination language(DDL)
   1-Create
   2-Reanme
   3-Alter
   4-Truncate
   5-Drop

2--Data manipulation language(DML)
  1-Insert
  2-Update
  3-Delete

3--Data control Language(DQL)
  1-Grant
  2-Revoke

4--Transition control Langauage(TCL)
   1-Commit
   2-Savepoint 
   3-Rollback

5-- Data Query language (DQL)
   1-Select
   2-Projection
   3-Selection
   4-Jions
